des:
SUCCESS LEAVES CLUES…

Welcome to LIFE HACKS with Maryleena, where Marlene Kristensen (aka Maryleena) shares some LIFE HACKS that have brought her from total (car)lifewreck to healthy, successful mompreneur.
If you want to work from home, need to boost your health, or feel like you have no real direction in life, this channel is for you.

Covering (but not limited to) WEALTH HACKS (Online Marketing / Personal Branding / Social Media / Content Creation / Coaching / Entrepreneurship), HEALTH HACKS (Wellness / Fitness / Health), and RANDOM HACKS (Life Experiences / Lessons Learned / Personal Development / Spirituality / Law of attraction).
